  "design_notes": "S0 (Intro): Sparsely paced steps building into light crossover jacks as vocal loops establish the rhythm. S1/S2 (Break): Complete stops-breather phrase to allow players to reset before the main drop. S3 (Drop Part 1): Heavy jumpstream and box movement patterns mirroring high-intensity vocal hits and synth stabs. S3 (Drop Part 2): Driving runningman patterns with light crossovers and sustained hold-taps for energetic pad play. S4 (Outro): Gentle fadeout with stops-breather to close.",
